---
layout: base
title: Writing
description: GTM intelligence, ICP methodology, and signal theory for B2B SaaS founders.
permalink: /blog/
---

<section class="blog-index">
  <div class="inner">

    <div class="blog-hd">
      <p class="eyebrow">Writing</p>
      <h1 class="sec-hl">THINKING.<br><em>OUT LOUD.</em></h1>
      <p class="blog-intro">GTM intelligence, ICP methodology, and signal theory. No frameworks for their own sake — only what increases clarity or resolves a constraint.</p>
    </div>

    {# ── Featured post (first/featured) ── #}
    {% set featuredPost = collections.featured[0] %}
    {% if featuredPost %}
    <div class="blog-featured">
      <a href="{{ featuredPost.url }}" class="post feat">
        <div class="ptag"><span class="ptag-dot"></span>Featured · {{ featuredPost.data.category }}</div>
        <div class="ptitle">{{ featuredPost.data.title }}</div>
        <div class="pexcerpt">{{ featuredPost.data.description }}</div>
        <div class="pmeta">
          <span>{{ featuredPost.date | postDate }} · {{ featuredPost.content | readingTime }}</span>
          <span class="pread">Read →</span>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
    {% endif %}

    {# ── All posts grid ── #}
    <div class="posts blog-grid">
      {% for post in collections.posts %}
        {% if not post.data.featured %}
        <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="post rv">
          <div class="ptag"><span class="ptag-dot"></span>{{ post.data.category }}</div>
          <div class="ptitle">{{ post.data.title }}</div>
          <div class="pexcerpt">{{ post.data.description }}</div>
          <div class="pmeta">
            <span>{{ post.date | postDate }} · {{ post.content | readingTime }}</span>
            <span class="pread">Read →</span>
          </div>
        </a>
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
